cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL, cs.HC 

The paper discusses the development and testing of a deep learning model for tuberculosis detection using chest X-ray images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the importance of considering technical specifications and disease severity distribution, which could fall under the human-computer interaction (cs.HC) sub-category.
